Comment: 0,0:00:01.90,0:00:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.99,0:00:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}稍微冷靜點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.76,0:00:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}差不多是你姐姐到車站的時間了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.74,0:00:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛的姐姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真是令人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}提比的表情就跟等待孫女到來的爺爺一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.05,0:00:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}感慨萬千
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}<OP>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}木製建築的小鎮 幾年不見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}和以前相比一點也沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Rabbit House在這條路的…
Comment: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}小兔子
Comment: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}小兔賽跑 好！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}等下～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}冷靜點啦
Comment: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯 嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不過 心愛的姐姐確實有點慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}本來這時候應該已經到了的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}明明地圖都給她畫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}或許是迷路了 我去找一下
Comment: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哇 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛別跟著迷路就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但是 剛來這個小鎮的時候 心愛明明老是迷路的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}感覺現在稍微變得可靠了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}喔 心愛發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}喂 你不要你姐姐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但是 好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}摸摸 摸摸 摸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你喜歡兔子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}櫻花樹的秘密你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}為什麼會綻放出美麗的粉色花朵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}稍微等下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你不會是打算講鬼故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是個非常悲傷的秘密喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那是怎樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我早就知道了 那個故事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不是有名的文學作品嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}才這點程度就想來嚇我什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗚嗚嗚嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 豆餡從天而降了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哇哇哇哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}千夜 紗路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}姐姐她沒來Rabbit House
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}話說就是今天來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是不是迷路了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}手機呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}姐姐她很不擅長機械 所以沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我們也一起去找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}能不能告訴我們是個怎樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個…是個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}因為那是姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}冷靜 心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這種傻裝不得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你還好意思說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我先模仿一下我姐姐好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}交給姐姐我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你這是在學自己？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這不就是平常的心愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嘛 原來是為了來看妹妹才千里迢迢的趕來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我妹妹她完全都不回家看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這次見面都已經時隔一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}久別重逢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}變裝一下偷偷的接近她 給她個驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好像會很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我最喜歡驚喜呀 還有整人之類的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真是個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那本書
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.83,0:06:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}充滿了驚喜和搗蛋情節
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}為什麼要烘培到這地步！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這台詞好帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}拍成電影後 我都哭了好幾次了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}而且
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}還聽說作者是這鎮上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那就是我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哦呀哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你想嚇到我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嘖嘖嘖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.82,0:07:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我才不會中招呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒回來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這裡就是Rabbit House
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這位客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}您怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}其實是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我完全都沒察覺到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}姐姐你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛真愛撒嬌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嘻嘻 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗚呼呼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.49,0:08:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Surprise
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}歡迎光…臨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛不在！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}請 請在自己喜歡的座位就坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}您想點些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那就
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}來一份原創混合咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}和心愛特製厚切吐司
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:09:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}混合咖啡和吐司 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}剛剛那孩子是智乃 還有提比
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那邊的女孩子是理世嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}大家都比照片上的還要可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}能讓人靜下心來的店面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咖啡的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛她…在廚房吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}還是說在休息呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}快點回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Surprise
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}看那樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是間諜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}也有可能是毒品走私販
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就沒有別的聯想了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}藝人呀 花粉症之類的 也是有可能的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯～真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛烤的麵包味道怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}香味合格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這麵包的口感不夠柔軟！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}客 客人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}白色的粉末
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}果然是毒品走私販啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}讓我來教教你們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}教 教什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真正的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真正的毒品走私販的可怕之處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}麵包真正的味道！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就用這小麥粉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}麵 麵包的味道？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}說是小麥粉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}肯定是某種暗號吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這個可疑的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}到底是誰啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我妹妹心愛受你們照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我是她姐姐摩卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛的姐姐呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛出去找我了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我都在信裡寫了不用擔心 在Rabbit House裡等就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是在什麼地方錯過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}還是那麼的馬虎眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你是理世吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}還有智乃和提比
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你們的事情我略有耳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}果然和心愛好像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}照片是隨著這麼大堆的信一起寄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那傢伙 都寄了些沒對焦的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}大家都很可愛 欸嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哪裡啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃國中就開始工作了真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}作為店主的孫女是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好可愛好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}理世也很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我 我已經是高中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}在我看起來就是很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}臉紅起來也很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.14,0:12:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好可愛好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個理世居然就這麼被摸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就好像受驚的兔子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.15,0:12:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}兔子的話這裡也有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要摸摸看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃真的好軟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}像媽媽一樣安詳的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃完全被俘獲了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}別躲了 過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}離我遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}理世～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我是不會淪陷的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}滿足了滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒事吧 理世
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我被摸摸什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}摩卡姐要去休息一下了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是啊 摩卡姐去心愛的房間休息吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:14:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒關係 心愛回來之前 我來店裡幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}呃 不能讓客人做這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}交給姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}令人信賴的姐姐的氣場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}平時心愛那麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:17.45,Default,,0,600,0,,{\be3}{\an8}交給姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就好像鬧劇一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}快好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好像做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這真的是小麥麵包嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}在閃閃發亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}上色了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:41.14,ZS,,0,0,0,,{\be3}ドリュール dorure 法語
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}雖然同是上色 但是看起來和平時心愛做的不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}開始吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}摩卡姐 這個麵包好吃的我都要哭出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}謝謝 智乃 理世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}什麼啊 沒必要去找嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛的姐姐已經和她們打成一片了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}和智乃及理世在一起 就像三姐妹一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}姐姐她…瞬間就把我作為姐姐的立場給…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好啦 我 我們也是三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}一起去征服天下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}謝謝千夜 紗路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:16:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但是 有點難進去的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}的確
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你回來了 心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}摩卡姐一直在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦 已經暴露了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}郵件裡的兔子很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你的變裝 太爛了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我之前也看到了一樣的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這麼有精神太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}姐姐～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}在大家面前太難為情了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我在這裡也是個可靠的姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}可靠的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}…姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}交給姐姐我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}想被表揚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就像搖著尾巴的小狗一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}趁著心愛也回來了 我也有件事情要報告
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}報告？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我要在Rabbit House這裡停留幾天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:18:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}已經事先得到店主許可了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}老夫可沒聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}一副「一定很驚訝吧」的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}的確能感到跟心愛有血緣關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}姐姐你時間很寬裕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那我去準備迎賓飲品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你們好 千夜 紗路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛的信裡寫了很多你們的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}都寫了些什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒寫什麼奇怪的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}說摸你們的時候手感都好舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}摸…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.63,0:18:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個 這是咖啡拉花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是心愛做的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真厲害 姐姐我好吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這是心愛成長的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}為了客人苦練許久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}到底是在練習咖啡拉花還是曬太陽呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不是該嘿嘿的問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好 今天允許你通宵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}太棒了 我有很多想聽的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對吧？ 智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我並沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我去倒點咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}聽我說聽我說 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯嗯 心愛冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}深呼吸一下再說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你瞞著我讓心愛的姐姐留宿了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}只是一點驚喜而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒想到吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}畢竟還有空房間 不用特意找住宿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}還可以跟心愛秉燭夜談
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}而且這樣智乃也能玩得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是這個意思吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就你來說這個驚喜還不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但也用不著瞞著我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}老爸你口風不嚴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那倒是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯？ 你小子是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:20:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這就是姐妹
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.55,0:23:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}店長 今天開始就要承蒙您關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}把這裡當成自己家就好
